  "title": "DeprecatedDecimalPipe",
  "contents": "\n\n<article>\n  <div class=\"page-actions\">\n    <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular/edit/master/packages/common/src/pipes/deprecated/number_pipe.ts?message=docs(common)%3A%20describe%20your%20change...#L61-L97\" aria-label=\"Suggest Edits\" title=\"Suggest Edits\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">mode_edit</i></a>\n    <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular/tree/6.0.0-beta.7/packages/common/src/pipes/deprecated/number_pipe.ts#L61-L97\" aria-label=\"View Source\" title=\"View Source\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">code</i></a>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"breadcrumb\">\n    <script type=\"application/ld+json\">\n      {\n        \"@context\": \"http://schema.org\",\n        \"@type\": \"BreadcrumbList\",\n        \"itemListElement\": [\n          { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 1, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io//api\", \"name\": \"API\" } },\n          { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 2, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api/common\", \"name\": \"@angular/common\" } },\n          { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 3, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api/common/DeprecatedDecimalPipe\", \"name\": \"DeprecatedDecimalPipe\" } }\n        ]\n      }\n    </script>\n      <a href=\"/api\">API</a> / <a href=\"api/common\">@angular/common</a>\n  </div>\n  <header class=\"api-header\">\n    <h1 id=\"deprecateddecimalpipe\">DeprecatedDecimalPipe<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/common/DeprecatedDecimalPipe#deprecateddecimalpipe\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n    <label class=\"api-type-label pipe\">pipe</label>\n    \n    \n    <label class=\"api-status-label stable\">stable</label>\n  </header>\n  <aio-toc class=\"embedded\"></aio-toc>\n\n  <div class=\"api-body\">\n    \n  <p class=\"short-description\"></p><p>Formats a number according to locale rules.</p>\n<p></p>\n  \n  \n  \n  \n\n  \n\n\n  \n<section class=\"usage-notes\">\n  <h2 id=\"usage-notes\">Usage Notes<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/common/DeprecatedDecimalPipe#usage-notes\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <p><code>number_expression | number[:digitInfo]</code></p>\n<p>Formats a number as text. Group sizing and separator and other locale-specific\nconfigurations are based on the active locale.</p>\n<p>where <code>expression</code> is a number:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><code>digitInfo</code> is a <code>string</code> which has a following format: <br>\n<code>{minIntegerDigits}.{minFractionDigits}-{maxFractionDigits}</code></li>\n<li><code>minIntegerDigits</code> is the minimum number of integer digits to use. Defaults to <code>1</code>.</li>\n<li><code>minFractionDigits</code> is the minimum number of digits after fraction. Defaults to <code>0</code>.</li>\n<li><code>maxFractionDigits</code> is the maximum number of digits after fraction. Defaults to <code>3</code>.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>For more information on the acceptable range for each of these numbers and other\ndetails see your native internationalization library.</p>\n<p>WARNING: this pipe uses the Internationalization API which is not yet available in all browsers\nand may require a polyfill. See <a href=\"guide/browser-support\">Browser Support</a> for details.</p>\n<h3 id=\"example\">Example<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/common/DeprecatedDecimalPipe#example\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h3>\n<code-example>\n@<a href=\"api/core/Component\" class=\"code-anchor\">Component</a>({\n  selector: 'deprecated-number-pipe',\n  template: `&#x3C;div>\n    &#x3C;p>e (no formatting): {{e}}&#x3C;/p>\n    &#x3C;p>e (3.1-5): {{e | number:'3.1-5'}}&#x3C;/p>\n    &#x3C;p>pi (no formatting): {{pi}}&#x3C;/p>\n    &#x3C;p>pi (3.5-5): {{pi | number:'3.5-5'}}&#x3C;/p>\n  &#x3C;/div>`\n})\nexport class DeprecatedNumberPipeComponent {\n  pi: number = 3.141592;\n  e: number = 2.718281828459045;\n}\n\n</code-example>\n\n</section>\n\n\n\n  </div>\n</article>\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - api/common\n - guide/browser-support\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - /api\n - api/common\n - api/common/DeprecatedDecimalPipe#deprecateddecimalpipe\n - api/common/DeprecatedDecimalPipe#example\n - api/common/DeprecatedDecimalPipe#usage-notes\n - api/core/Component\n - guide/browser-support\n - https://github.com/angular/angular/edit/master/packages/common/src/pipes/deprecated/number_pipe.ts?message=docs(common)%3A%20describe%20your%20change...#L61-L97\n - https://github.com/angular/angular/tree/6.0.0-beta.7/packages/common/src/pipes/deprecated/number_pipe.ts#L61-L97\n-->"
